I have nothing against PvPers, I used to play PvP (VZ) but it starts here and ends with every server having a forum.  I just don't see that PvPers need another place to post, like all the other forums aren't good enough.  Besides the fact that PvP represents such a small portion of our 10000+ users.<br>
<br>
It wouldn't bother me, personally, if there was a PvP forum. Voting no on my own accord would just be out of spite, and that's not the way I work. But I'm thinking from a mod stand-point that's it's just one more forum to moderate, as well as the fact that we've seen some PvP threads turn into roleplaying nightmares in the past.<br>
<br>
*shrug*<br>
