<br>
Pros: Facilitate discussion and reading of posts specific to PvP<br>
Cons: ... Any?<br>
<br>
My one concern, has to do with the fact that the Rogue is somewhat of an underdog in the PvP game.  He must rely on superior knowledge, trickery, and skill to overcome the point-and-click caster attack.  Having a wide open forum  has a flipside in that players of other classes *whistles nonchalantly* will be scanning this forum to gain an edge over rogues.  Experienced players may be hesitant to relate useful tricks in this scenario.<br>
<br>
If there are plans to resume the registration of rogues to the root cellar then the "Mimic" function makes it a simple matter to copy the user list to the PvP forum when changes are made.  <br>
